    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After discussing with @rayrutjes he seems to have a pretty solid implementation (without InstantSearch.js). His menu fetches first \"all the values\" with a request using search for facet values. There are no subsequent updates but we could imagine doing a rendering to display the counts. The order is based on the count (most used facet value first).\r\n\r\nThat could be the target behavior.",
