    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Another example where I wanted to submit items manually:\r\n- https://discourse.algolia.com/t/defining-ranges-for-priceranges-widget/4219/4\r\n- solution: https://codesandbox.io/s/mo0wrpm24x\r\n\r\nThe solution is not complete at all, it would require:\r\n- graying option that are not relevant\r\n- having the manual inputs\r\n\r\nWhich is why I believe this would make a good candidate for a true feature, ultimately I would have been pleased to be able to do:\r\n\r\n```js\r\npriceRanges({\r\n  items: [{to: 12}, {from: 12, to: 30}, {to: 50}]\r\n})\r\n```",
